Movie Review

Well this 1 hour movie is spoiled right of way because it is Czech and comes up under the Czech search which it is but it has been for some reason translated to Spanish which makes this a comedy again. Second issue is its somewhat unreal behavior in the plot and more importantly how many mechanics that you know are gay? I have never come across that. Otherwise its a choppy video and sound and I gave up on actually watching it and just fast forwarded it and I had enough. 

Video: 5 out of 10
Sound: 5 out of 10

Poor scores due to skipping at least when played through GOM Player, KMP Player, and Dziobas Rar Player. However, if you can with with the occasional skipping and Spanish then it is good quality video.

PS: Must agree with Asianrice; if people are homophobic then why the hell do they even run a gay search and if they come to this by accident, like me when running a Czech search, then why actually download it and watch it?  I don't have an issue with it and I am straight who watches just about anything and then I review it for fun although this was a little too much for me.
